Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:37.98,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,30)\fad(700,700)}漫游字幕组\N{\fsp0\fnArial\fs32\b0}http://bbs.popgo.org/
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========PREV=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的演讲稿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读读吧阿斯特莱雅 来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 别那么大嗓门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把孩子都吵醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样 只是在要求扩大自治权
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次演讲应该成为向地球圈的宣战！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却不能把它化成语言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你累了 休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去躺一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我去睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还怎么唤醒我的弟子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯特莱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天就会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拉上各各他的刑场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:07.57,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\an8\blur3\fs56}各各他：Gogltha 耶稣基督被钉死之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后从十字架上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触怒盖亚的罪人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将被业火焚身 死灭殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小会儿也好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 阿尔黛西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 晚安…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OPCN=========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:05.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即使是无尽的苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:16.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}无垠的太空也能够包容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:32.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}紧锁心灵的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:39.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}也有解开的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:46.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}洋溢而出的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:50.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}与近在咫尺的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:58.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}难以抑制的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:05.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在星辰坠落的寂静宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:12.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}飘忽的永恒时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:19.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}甚至连光都能超越
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:25.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}向那未来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========TEXT==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:21.41,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs74\fad(2300,600)\an5\b1\bord2\blur2\pos(960,910)}机动战士高达 起源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:26.33,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.35\fs70\fad(600,0)\an5\b0\bord5\blur2\3c&H2100CF&\pos(960,910)\fsp6}前夜 赤色彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:35.34,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,1050)\fs70\fsp2\bord2\blur5\pos(1587,926)\3c&H171719&}吉翁之子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁·兹姆·戴肯议长即将发表演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长是否会宣布从联邦独立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界的人们都在关注
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请退后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 阿尔黛西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴肯！戴肯！戴肯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要见议长！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴肯到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反对联邦的蛮横
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我们受了多少罪吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要听议长的演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要独立！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长心脏病突发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽经全力抢救…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他最后嘱咐我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾好阿斯特莱雅夫人和孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事请尽管开口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为跟随戴肯最久的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下德金·扎比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将携整个家族为您效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的示威铺天盖地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴肯的死应该是机密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有人故意走漏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多半是老二萨斯罗派人干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德金向来视戴肯为眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以派人下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在孩子们面前别说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 孩子们更应该清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的父亲是被杀的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被扎比家的那伙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可贸然行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请先到寒舍安顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是犬子兰巴·拉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会带路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把他当作您的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常光荣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够为戴肯家的各位效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\blur2\b0}（特别出口）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许阻拦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面左转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然跑到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把路让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好豪华的车 里面是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁 是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是戴肯一家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不听话我真开枪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很为难啊 兰巴·拉尔上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基西莉亚·扎比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来帮你吧 无偿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是基西莉亚小姐吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…何等威武
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您言下之意我不像个妇人是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎比家风如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但笑无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么放他走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和兰巴·拉尔抢人有失体面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着戴肯的遗孤被抢走…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨斯罗哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必动手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不许插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易操纵舆论让人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联邦杀死了戴肯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却中了那个老头子的奸计
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说那个老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送拉尔一家上路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最终目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们理想的具现者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大的慕佐领导人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁·兹姆·戴肯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慕佐议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为宇宙移民争取解放的先驱者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被上苍召唤 化为一块基石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿他的灵魂安宁 大义长存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿他的理想永在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便肉体腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的精神仍会照亮我们前路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨斯罗哥哥 那有点过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 你是说基西莉亚的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不到动手的地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还嫌不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近她太得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是手足 以和为贵嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多兹鲁！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后的政界将是一场血腥厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基西莉亚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多兹鲁大哥他们的车…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这么点事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是扎比家的男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭火 快灭火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨斯罗哥哥死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁干的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.30,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(400,400)\bord3\blur3\fs60}萨斯罗·扎比遭暗杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.39,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(400,400)\bord3\blur3\fs60}政敌拉尔家与之关联？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:21.78,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(400,900)\bord3\blur3\fs60}戴肯刚死 权力之争即现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼念吉翁·兹姆·戴肯的葬礼车队发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身处车内的萨斯罗·扎比氏当场死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同乘的多兹鲁·扎比氏奇迹般生还
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡编乱造！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽向扎比家摇尾示好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是德金的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他害怕暗杀戴肯的罪行暴露 为转移视线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死自己的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我们背这个黑锅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会这样吗 父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 连你也怀疑我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭这点理由 至于杀自己的儿子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨斯罗不讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有才干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在扎比家也深得器重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰巴阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯特莱雅夫人找您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然绑架戴肯家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有脸见戴肯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉尔上尉求见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我非常理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊 人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 上尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法没人照料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法是只猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法最怕孤单了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人抱着它就不敢入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连上厕所 都要人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔一定带回那只路西法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰巴·拉尔叔叔 没有办不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执行营救路西法作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路西法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉 你叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 在下多诺瓦·马特格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上一支小队 跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记告诉叔叔 路西法会抓陌生人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把拉尔家族赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德金·扎比万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀光拉尔家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨斯罗的血债
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:14.68,note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,500)\bord3\blur3\fs60}扎比！扎比！扎比…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们战胜拉尔家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市陷入疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一味煽动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该收则收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民众在高呼您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给联邦不必要的口实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基连哥哥 父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们原来在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太愉快太痛快了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等不及看拉尔家下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多兹鲁 你已经好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我浑身血脉偾张 根本睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了给萨斯罗哥哥昭雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用这双手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠逼急了也会咬猫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金巴·拉尔已经一只脚踏进棺材了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有他的儿子兰巴·拉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在慕佐卫队的年轻士官中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是颇有威望的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基连 你需要学会多一点城府
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰巴·拉尔确实是个人才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是拉尔家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至想让他当部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人留个台阶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宽容是胜利者的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴肯和金巴·拉尔都已经成为过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有扎比家族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能为今后的历史负责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道今天是什么日子吗 老头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 这家店今天已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…上尉阁下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大喊大叫的 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫…塔克？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上还给夜店当保镖？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚特别危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是出于自愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎啊 上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯兰普 你这酒保越做越像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 不打算回军队了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么军队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给联邦军打杂而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 上尉如果有请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时整装待发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈蒙小姐 客人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 别放人进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天这妆化得也是绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是妆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被路西法那小东西挠的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候还有闲心拈花惹草？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个什么样的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…身手敏捷的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈蒙 对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有事麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想送一个人去地球逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲金巴·拉尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然什么事都瞒不过你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然出了萨斯罗这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸肯定没活路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能眼睁睁看他被扎比家整死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有的是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在不行一口咬住他们的七寸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去地球…就你父亲一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还会带上更麻烦的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…要是用上港务局的门路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等你这句话！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那少尉又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种单纯的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别让他当真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为什么要生为戴肯的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许继续靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保安队队长基西莉亚·扎比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有要事来访
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金巴·拉尔阁下不见任何扎比家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今我也不想看见金巴·拉尔那张老脸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为新议长 德金·扎比的代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事求见卡斯帕尔·雷姆·戴肯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰巴在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 去城里喝酒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种关键时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基西莉亚我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很强悍的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 扎比家是父亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅少爷休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事关重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且非你我不能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在城里一片骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受伤 有人丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是因为你们杀了我的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事是谁教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是金巴·拉尔灌输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基西莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有事和我谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果继续用这种教训孩子的口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恕不奉陪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回房休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那让我们回到正题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有为戴肯家族建造的豪宅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你们一家三口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样萨斯罗的事就一笔勾销
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会让城里恢复平静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 决不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们三个一旦离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉尔家会被赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 我要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你果真信守诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:21:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说萨斯罗先生的事一笔勾销
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 杀我父亲的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让它一笔勾销！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还纠缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有响声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡斯帕尔有危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.59,0:22:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才为什么不出声？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全可以呼救的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说 你不怕我？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以为没人敢冒犯你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡斯帕尔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋味如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以把你作为犯人投进大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是戴肯的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不能对我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德金·扎比才是现在这个国家里最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德金只要一声令下 照样能办你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我是吉翁·兹姆·戴肯的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我长大 马上就能让你们再听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡斯帕尔·雷姆·戴肯命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它解开！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//=============EDCN=============
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:31.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:37.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}人总要历经悲伤才能成长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:46.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}而今 我的爱人因寂寞而颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:52.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}那份哀伤依旧在我心头徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:54.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:24:01.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}泪水啊 请回归大海
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:11.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}日思夜想的爱恋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.54,0:24:20.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}天空逐渐染成暗红
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:28.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}啊 我的爱 我的挚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.79,0:24:32.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}我好想再次回到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.93,0:24:38.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}我的爱人 再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.06,0:24:43.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}啊 我的爱 我的挚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.10,0:24:48.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}我好想再次回到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.30,0:24:56.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(200,200)\blur2\pos(960,1028)}没有人能在孤单里存活下去
